OL,3,CCarrie Johnson warns mothers about
OL,4,Cdehydration after hospitalisation
OL,6,FCarrie Johnson has urged breastfeeding
OL,7,Fmothers to eat and drink properly
OL,8,Fafter she was hospitalised with severe
OL,9,Fdehydration.
OL,11,FThe wife of former prime minister
OL,12,FBoris Johnson, whose fourth child with
OL,13,Fhim was born on May 21, said a two-
OL,14,Fnight hospital stay was "not on my
OL,15,Fpostpartum bingo card".
OL,17,FShe posted an Instagram story
OL,18,Falongside a photo of Mrs Johnson in
OL,19,Fhospital cradling baby Poppy Eliza
OL,20,FJosephine.
