OL,3,CCarrie Johnson warns mothers about
OL,4,Cdehydration after hospitalisation
OL,6,FIt comes as Britain faces another
OL,7,Fheatwave this weekend, triggering an
OL,8,Famber health alert amid warnings
OL,9,Ftemperatures could top 30C.
OL,11,FMrs Johnson wrote: "Being hospitalised
OL,12,Ffor two nights for severe dehydration
OL,13,Fwas not on my postpartum bingo card."
OL,15,FShe urged "breastfeeding mums" to make
OL,16,Fsure they eat and drink enough,
OL,17,F"especially if your babe is
OL,18,Fclusterfeeding".
