OL,3,CCarrie Johnson warns mothers about
OL,4,Cdehydration after hospitalisation
OL,6,FHer message comes as a second amber
OL,7,Fheat health alert in two weeks came
OL,8,Finto force on Friday.
OL,10,FThe alert, which covers London, the
OL,11,FEast Midlands, South East, South West
OL,12,Fand East of England, will last until
OL,13,F6pm on Tuesday.
OL,15,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,16,Fhas also issued a yellow alert for
OL,17,FYorkshire and Humber and the West
OL,18,FMidlands for the same time period,
OL,19,Fwith the agency warning of significant
OL,20,Fimpacts across health and social care
OL,21,Fservices.
